---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="About | Marco Schneider"
    description="Full Stack Web Developer with experience in scalable solutions, Angular, .NET/C#, and robotics."
>
    <article class="about">
        <header class="about-header">
            <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
            <h1>Hey, I'm Marco.</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Full Stack Web Developer & Systems Engineer</p>
        </header>

        <div class="about-body">
            <section class="about-section glass-panel">
                <h2>Background</h2>
                <p>
                    I am a Full Stack Web Developer with a proven track record of delivering scalable, production-grade solutions in agile corporate environments. I specialize in building robust applications from end to end using <strong>Angular, .NET/C#, Azure, and SQL Server</strong>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Beyond traditional web development, I have a strong background in <strong>robotics, embedded systems, and applied research</strong>. My experience includes technical laboratory work and leadership roles in university competition teams, where I developed embedded control systems and processed real-time sensor data.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section glass-panel">
                <h2>Experience & Approach</h2>
                <p>
                    I excel at transforming complex business requirements into reliable, maintainable software. I have extensive experience in <strong>feature development, technical debt management, and CI/CD automation</strong>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Collaboration is at the core of my work style. I frequently partner with Business Analysts and cross-functional teams, and I'm deeply committed to mentoring peers through knowledge-transfer sessions to maintain high standards of code quality across the board.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section glass-panel">
                <h2>Core Technologies</h2>
                <div class="tech-stack">
                    <span class="tech-badge">Angular</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">.NET / C#</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">Azure</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">SQL Server</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">GitHub CI/CD</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">TypeScript</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">C++ / Embedded</span>
                    <span class="tech-badge">ROS</span>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section glass-panel">
                <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
                <ul class="links-list">
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">GitHub</a> — open source work and side projects
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> — professional history
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a> — subscribe to the blog</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .about {
        padding: 52px 0;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .eyebrow {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        color: var(--accent-main);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .about-header {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .about-header h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .about-body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 24px;
    }
    .about-section {
        padding: 32px;
    }
    .about-section h2 {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--accent-main);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about-section p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .about-section p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .about-section strong {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .tech-stack {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
    }
    .tech-badge {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 500;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    
    .links-list {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .links-list a {
        color: var(--accent-main);
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.2s, text-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .links-list a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-secondary);
        text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-glow);
    }
</style>
